# ============================================
# NUTRIO ENVIRONMENT CONFIGURATION
# ============================================
#
# This file contains all environment variables needed to run Nutrio.
# Follow the setup instructions below to configure your local environment.
#
# ‚ö†Ô∏è  IMPORTANT: Never commit your actual .env file with real credentials!
# ============================================

# --------------------------------------------
# 1. FIREBASE CONFIGURATION (REQUIRED)
# --------------------------------------------
# Firebase provides authentication, database (Firestore), and file storage.
# Get your credentials from: https://console.firebase.google.com/
#
# Setup Instructions:
# 1. Go to https://console.firebase.google.com/
# 2. Create a new project (or select an existing one)
# 3. Click the gear icon ‚öôÔ∏è  ‚Üí Project Settings
# 4. Scroll down to "Your apps" section
# 5. Click the Web icon (</>) to create a web app
# 6. Copy the config values and paste them below
#
# Cost: FREE tier includes:
#   - 50,000 reads/day
#   - 20,000 writes/day
#   - 1GB storage
#   - Plenty for personal use!

VITE_FIREBASE_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
VITE_FIREBASE_AUTH_DOMAIN=your_project_id.firebaseapp.com
VITE_FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=your_project_id
VITE_FIREBASE_STORAGE_BUCKET=your_project_id.appspot.com
VITE_FIREBASE_MESSAGING_SENDER_ID=your_sender_id
VITE_FIREBASE_APP_ID=your_app_id

# Example (DO NOT USE - these are fake credentials):
# VITE_FIREBASE_API_KEY=AIzaSyA1234567890abcdefghijklmnopqrst
# VITE_FIREBASE_AUTH_DOMAIN=nutrio-app-123.firebaseapp.com
# VITE_FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=nutrio-app-123
# VITE_FIREBASE_STORAGE_BUCKET=nutrio-app-123.appspot.com
# VITE_FIREBASE_MESSAGING_SENDER_ID=123456789012
# VITE_FIREBASE_APP_ID=1:123456789012:web:a1b2c3d4e5f6g7h8i9

# --------------------------------------------
# 2. GOOGLE GEMINI AI API (REQUIRED)
# --------------------------------------------
# Gemini AI powers all smart features in Nutrio:
#   ‚úì Meal photo analysis
#   ‚úì Fridge ingredient scanning
#   ‚úì Smart meal suggestions
#   ‚úì Weekly AI-generated personalized meal plans
#   ‚úì Nutritional insights
#
# Get your FREE API key:
# 1. Visit https://makersuite.google.com/app/apikey
# 2. Sign in with your Google account
# 3. Click "Create API Key"
# 4. Copy and paste below
#
# Cost: 100% FREE
# Free Tier Limits (very generous):
