# --------------------------------------------
# 4. SENTRY ERROR MONITORING (OPTIONAL - RECOMMENDED FOR PRODUCTION)
# --------------------------------------------
# Sentry tracks errors and performance in production.
# Helps you catch bugs before users report them.
#
